import OrderManagement   from './admin/OrderManagement';   // ‡∏´‡∏ô‡πâ‡∏≤‡πÄ‡∏î‡∏¥‡∏°: ‡∏à‡∏±‡∏î‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏Ñ‡∏≥‡∏™‡∏±‡πà‡∏á‡∏ã‡∏∑‡πâ‡∏≠
import Login             from './auth/Login';              // ‡∏´‡∏ô‡πâ‡∏≤‡πÄ‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏™‡∏π‡πà‡∏£‡∏∞‡∏ö‡∏ö
import Addresses         from './account/Addresses';       // ‡∏´‡∏ô‡πâ‡∏≤: ‡∏à‡∏±‡∏î‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏≠‡∏¢‡∏π‡πà‡∏ú‡∏π‡πâ‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ
import Register          from './auth/Register';           // ‚úÖ ‡∏´‡∏ô‡πâ‡∏≤: ‡∏™‡∏°‡∏±‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏™‡∏°‡∏≤‡∏ä‡∏¥‡∏Å
import VariantsManager   from './admin/VariantsManager';
import OptionsPage       from './admin/OptionsPage.js';

// ‚úÖ ‡∏ï‡∏±‡πâ‡∏á baseURL + ‡πÅ‡∏ô‡∏ö token ‚Äî ‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏≠‡∏¢‡∏π‡πà "‡∏´‡∏•‡∏±‡∏á import ‡∏ó‡∏±‡πâ‡∏á‡∏´‡∏°‡∏î"
axios.defaults.baseURL = process.env.REACT_APP_API_BASEURL || 'http://localhost:3001';
const bootToken = localStorage.getItem('token');
if (bootToken) {
  axios.defaults.headers.common['Authorization'] = `Bearer ${bootToken}`;
}

// ===========================
// ‡∏™‡∏ß‡∏¥‡∏ï‡∏ä‡πå‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡πå‡∏î‡∏™‡∏¥‡∏ó‡∏ò‡∏¥‡πå
// ===========================
const ENABLE_AUTH_GUARD = false;
const getToken = () => localStorage.getItem('token');

// ===========================
// ‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡πå‡∏î‡∏™‡∏¥‡∏ó‡∏ò‡∏¥‡πå
// ===========================
function RequireAuth({ children }) {
  if (!ENABLE_AUTH_GUARD) return children;              // ‡πÇ‡∏´‡∏°‡∏î dev: ‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡πÄ‡∏ä‡πá‡∏Ñ token
  const token = getToken();
  if (!token) return <Navigate to="/login" replace />;  // ‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏°‡∏µ token ‚Üí ‡πÑ‡∏õ‡∏•‡πá‡∏≠‡∏Å‡∏≠‡∏¥‡∏ô
  return children;                                      // ‡∏°‡∏µ token ‚Üí ‡πÄ‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≤‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ
}

// ===========================
// Navbar
// ===========================
function Navbar() {
  const nav = useNavigate();

  const linkStyle = ({ isActive }) => ({
    textDecoration: 'none',
    padding: '6px 10px',
    borderRadius: 8,
    background: isActive ? '#f0f0f0' : 'transparent',
  });

  const hasToken = !!getToken();

  function logout() {
    localStorage.removeItem('token');
    delete axios.defaults.headers.common['Authorization'];
    nav('/login', { replace: true });
  }

  return (
    <nav style={{ padding: 10, display: 'flex', gap: 16, borderBottom: '1px solid #eee' }}>
      <NavLink to="/" style={linkStyle} end>‡∏™‡∏¥‡∏ô‡∏Ñ‡πâ‡∏≤</NavLink>
      <NavLink to="/admin/orders" style={linkStyle}>‡∏Ñ‡∏≥‡∏™‡∏±‡πà‡∏á‡∏ã‡∏∑‡πâ‡∏≠</NavLink>
      <NavLink to="/account/addresses" style={linkStyle}>‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏≠‡∏¢‡∏π‡πà‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏â‡∏±‡∏ô</NavLink>

      <div style={{ marginLeft: 'auto', display: 'flex', gap: 8 }}>
        {!hasToken ? (
          <>
            <NavLink to="/login" style={linkStyle}>‡πÄ‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏™‡∏π‡πà‡∏£‡∏∞‡∏ö‡∏ö</NavLink>
            <NavLink to="/register" style={linkStyle}>‡∏™‡∏°‡∏±‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏™‡∏°‡∏≤‡∏ä‡∏¥‡∏Å</NavLink>
          </>
        ) : (
          <button onClick={logout} style={{ padding: '6px 10px', borderRadius: 8 }}>
            ‡∏≠‡∏≠‡∏Å‡∏à‡∏≤‡∏Å‡∏£‡∏∞‡∏ö‡∏ö
          </button>
        )}
      </div>
    </nav>
  );
}

// ===========================
// ‡πÅ‡∏≠‡∏õ‡∏´‡∏•‡∏±‡∏Å
// ===========================
export default function App() {
  useEffect(() => {
    const t = getToken();
    if (t) axios.defaults.headers.common['Authorization'] = `Bearer ${t}`;
  }, []);

  return (
    <BrowserRouter>
      <Navbar />

      <Routes>
        {/* ‡∏´‡∏ô‡πâ‡∏≤‡πÅ‡∏£‡∏Å: ‡∏£‡∏∞‡∏ö‡∏ö‡∏à‡∏±‡∏î‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏™‡∏¥‡∏ô‡∏Ñ‡πâ‡∏≤ */}
